About Us

Somerset Re provides customized risk management solutions to the life insurance and annuity sectors.
 
We specialize in reinsurance solutions that help our clients efficiently deploy capital, improve long-term performance and fund new business growth. Our team of highly experienced reinsurance professionals customizes each reinsurance program to optimize the benefits for our clients.


 









Solutions
Somerset Re provides risk management solutions for interest sensitive and capital intensive lines of business.
  
 





Our Core Strengths include: 

Asset management
Product risk and liability management
Reinsurance market innovation and transaction design
Senior team with deep global reinsurance experience







Our customized transactions allow our clients to:

Release embedded value on in-force, non-core lines of business
Improve long term return on equity
Improve regulatory and rating agency capital ratios
Access fresh, high quality reinsurance capacity







Our solutions are ideally suited for:

Interest Sensitive Life Insurance
COLI / BOLI Products
Indexed Life Insurance and Annuity Products
Fixed Deferred, Immediate and Multi-Year Guarantee Annuities
Structured Settlements







 










 

Experience
Our team has deep experience in capital markets, actuarial risk modeling, reinsurance structuring and investments. Collectively, we have successfully executed hundreds of cross-border reinsurance transactions.




 













