Company Description


Somerset Re Ltd. provides risk management solutions to the life insurance and annuity sectors. It provides asset management, product risk and liability management, reinsurance market innovation and transaction design solutions. The company was founded by Stephen Gallant and Brian Holland and is headquartered in Pembroke, Bermuda.




