Atlas Merchant Capital LLC

                                    Atlas Merchant Capital seeks investment opportunities in companies located across the globe. The firm focuses on capital-intensive businesses in developed markets, specifically in the United States, Canada, Western Europe and Japan. They targets companies operating in the fields of financial services. They brings a competitive advantage to areas of growth and opportunity.                                




